{"about_the_game":"In this game, players embark on a maritime journey, sailing across the vast ocean to assist communities living on the water. Using modular blocks, players construct various buildings and homes. Throughout the building process, players will face natural disasters such as tornadoes, earthquakes, and thunderstorms, which have realistic, physics-based effects on the structures. Players must balance stability and aesthetics to create safe and beautiful homes for the people they meet along the way. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdditionally, the game features a Painter Mode that allows players to use acquired color palettes to repaint their already constructed buildings. This mode encourages players to fully unleash their imagination and creativity, giving each structure a unique and personalized touch.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734591970","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837740/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734591970","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837740/83827b361961e51bccc7877d66c1d835a4a4fa54/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734591970","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837740/83827b361961e51bccc7877d66c1d835a4a4fa54/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734591970","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3178990,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"In this game, players embark on a maritime journey, sailing across the vast ocean to assist communities living on the water. Using modular blocks, players construct various buildings and homes. Throughout the building process, players will face natural disasters such as tornadoes, earthquakes, and thunderstorms, which have realistic, physics-based effects on the structures. Players must balance stability and aestheti